      "writtenOn": "2020-05-12T14:59:07Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Right now, all GrDawnRenderTargets have only a view (not just GrBackendRenderTarget), so any readbacks from render targets will fail. Assuming we can live with this limitation long-term in Skia, I was thinking also that a cap would be a good idea.\n\nSounds like this is a GrBackendTexture, though, so that\u0027s a bit confusing.",
      "parentUuid": "c0dc0a36_49e7d8b8",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 852,
        "startChar": 13,
        "endLine": 852,
        "endChar": 23
