      "writtenOn": "2020-05-12T15:34:16Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Reading your comment a bit more carefully: creating a GrDawnRenderTarget from a GrBackendTexture will strip the dawn::Texture out of it, and leave only a dawn::TextureView. So you couldn\u0027t do readbacks from it. I think Brian mentioned that this code path was deprecated, though?",
